Paper: hep-th/0211108

Date: 2002-11-12

Title: Multi-Instanton Calculus and Equivariant Cohomology

Authors: Ugo Bruzzo, Francesco Fucito, Jose F. Morales, Alessandro Tanzini

Comments: 29 pages, some conventions changed and some typos corrected

We present a systematic derivation of multi-instanton amplitudes in terms ofADHM equivariant cohomology. The results rely on a supersymmetric formulationof the localization formula for equivariant forms. We examine the cases of N=4and N=2 gauge theories with adjoint and fundamental matter.